## Defining the Blueprint

To create a blueprint, use the keyword `class` followed by a capitalized name.

```dart
// This is just a blueprint. Nothing is actually created yet!
class Player {
  // We will define what a player looks like in the next lesson!
}
```
Note: Class names always start with a **Capital Letter** (like `String`).

